## 12. Conclusion

The Smart City Complaint Analysis project successfully transformed complaint data into meaningful insights. By analyzing complaint trends, resolution efficiency, hotspot zones, and department performance, city authorities can improve service delivery, increase citizen satisfaction, and support evidence-based urban planning. The dashboard provides a comprehensive decision-support system for smart city governance.
